      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MISS JO (3) had been racing in honest fashion recording two placings in a row before finishing fourth (23.07) at this track latest. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Ready to return to form. DID SO (5) comes off an average effort last start when sixth at this track over 400m behind Aston Yamato (23.12) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. PAW GELDOFF (1) missed the frame latest when eighth at Ballarat (26.23) but scored four back at The Meadows (30.35). Should be about the mark. WESTSIDE WIZARD (2) profiles nicely here at this trip.",
